  "texts": [
    "We classified participants as compliant with the AI assessment if they showed compliance in at least one of the three incorrect trials.",
    "We expected the Judgment→AIsupport group to be less compliant than the AIsupport→Judgment group.",
    "Although we had not found this difference between groups in Experiment 1 due to the low compliance rate in both groups in that study, we expected to observe this result in Experiment 2, as we increased the sample size and the number of incorrect trials.",
    "We conducted a chi-square test to analyze the difference between groups in participants' compliance.",
    "We did not find a statistically significant difference in compliance between groups, χ 2 (1) = 0.37, p = 0.545, Cramer's V = 0.04."
  ],
